campaign_details: Looking for Music influencers who can use our new music app and give reviews accordingly.

Wipro is planning to launch a music application. We are looking for influencers in the following fields:

- Music: Influencers interested in music (singers, instrumentalists, DJs, etc) can apply. 
- Fashion: Fashion influencers are required for the promotional photoshoot. 
- Photography: Photography influencers are required for the promotional photoshoot scheduled for the launch of our app.
Allen Solly is looking for fashion influencers to promote our upcoming Winter Collection, scheduled to release in November.
Allen Solly believes in diversity. We are planning to do a special photoshoot with influencers for our Pride Month Special video.
Allen Solly is looking for photographers to cover our Winter Collection photoshoot
